<br>
Thanes are sort of the shadowknights of DAOC.  That is they are a good R v R class and good P v E class--but they do less damage than all the other melee classes (except the skald) in melee.  Their AE nukes are effective because of the number of thanes, but they actually dish out less damage than their straight up melee.  But thanes can rack up a lot of points in R v R.<br>
<br>
Two classes have AE damage spells.<br>
Runemasters, who apparently can outdamage the nukers of other realms but are generally rarely played, and thanes, who are probably the most plentiful class in the realm on my server.  Shaman have an AE dot, but cave magic is considered a bad choice, and so you will probably never encounter this.  <br>
<br>
Two classes have AE mez abilities.<br>
Healers and spiritmasters, but spiritmasters are not known to use these spells.  Skalds have a single target mez which I don't recall seeing used in R v R.<br>
<br>
Three classes have movement speed spells.<br>
Healers (slowest, most usually at 25% or so), then runemasters (40% or faster I think), then skalds.  Hunters have an escape shout as well.   <br>
<br>
Healers can be identified by the fact they use hammers, and carry a small shield.  Thanes use med shields, warriors can use the tower ones.  Of course, warriors, thanes, and skalds can all use hammers, and some end up doing so, so it's not always easy to tell which is a healer.<br>
<br>
Shaman have poorer offensive abilities than healers, who can buff themselves up to do 50+ damage a hit with 25%+ haste at 30, so shaman have little purpose besides buffing and healing since the debuff nerf.  To mock shaman, healers receive haste spells, speed buffs, clarity, slows, mezzes and stuns.  Shaman get better root spells which are too slow to cast in battle.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
Healers and shaman have the same hp pool as the tanks. <br>
<br>
Skalds have fewer hp, about the same as the rogues.  Dwarves can be runemasters, and may occasionally have more HP than the shadowblade kobolds.  <br>
<br>
I believe the epic weapons are purple in color, not completely sure.  <br>
<br>
Hunters are the only class that can use a spear.  Only hunters can charm, and this is limited to animals.  No class has a spell that replenishes endurance.<br>
<br>
Midgard on my server seems to have two shortcomings.  First, the number of stealth class members seems to be low.  Second, they are short on healer/rezzers.  I attribute this to the Midgard tank mentality.  A lot of people go to midgard to play tanks.<br>
<br>
In order of popularity, it seems to go like this:<br>
<br>
Thanes<br>
Zerkers<br>
Hunters<br>
Healers<br>
followed far behind by:<br>
<br>
Warriors<br>
Skalds<br>
Runemasters<br>
Shaman<br>
Shadowblades<br>
Spiritmasters <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulisboa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lisboa</A> at: 2/4/02 6:18:48 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showMessageRange?topicID=2004.topic&start=21&stop=28>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=2004.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showNextMessage?topicID=2004.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2004.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=2004.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.threadControl?topicID=2004.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2004.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2004.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<optio